        public static Iterator<?> getAllElementsIterator​(EventSource session,
                                                 CollectionType collectionType,
                                                 Object collection)
        Given a collection, get an iterator of all its children, loading them from the database if necessary.
        Parameters:

        Returns:

                                                    CollectionType collectionType,
